# Playwright E2E Testing

End-to-end testing with Playwright. Write reliable browser tests for web applications.

## Patterns
- Use Page Object Model for reusable page interactions
- Test critical user flows (login, registration, checkout)
- Use `test.describe` for grouping related tests
- Use `test.use` for fixture configuration
- Run in CI with `playwright install --with-deps`
- Use trace viewer for debugging failures
